-- City Lodge Buys 50% Stake in Fairview to Expand in East Africa
-- B y   N a s r e e n   S e r i a
-- 2012-05-30T05:11:40Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-05-30/city-lodge-buys-50-stake-in-fairview-to-expand-in-east-africa.html
City Lodge Hotels Ltd. (CLH)  said it
acquired a 50 percent stake in Fairview Hotel, which owns two
hotels in Nairobi.  The company will seek further expansion in East Africa,
with potential sites identified in Kenya, Tanzania, Rwanda and
Uganda.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Nasreen Seria at 
 nseria@bloomberg.net  